=Analyze this video transcript and identify ONLY the ELITE clips worthy of posting as short-form content (TikTok, Instagram Reels, YouTube Shorts).

**Video Title:** {{ $('Get a record4').item.json['Title 1'] }}

**Video Summary:** {{ $('Get a record4').item.json['Video summary'] }}

**Full Transcript with Timestamps:**
{{ $json.Transcript }}

**CRITICAL:** Quality over quantity. Only select clips that meet ALL criteria and would genuinely perform well. If you only find 1-2 elite clips, that's perfectly fine. If you find zero clips that meet the standards, return an empty array.

Do NOT force clips that don't meet the criteria. Every clip you identify must be excellent and self-contained.

Return your response as a JSON array of clips.
